{
  "video_id": "XowcxCYbug0",
  "title": "How video games turn players into storytellers | David Cage",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12869.0,
      "end_time": 17559.0,
      "text": "The way we tell stories has naturally changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17583.0,
      "end_time": 20723.0,
      "text": "since Aristotle defined the rules of tragedy"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20748.0,
      "end_time": 23169.0,
      "text": "about 2,500 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24264.0,
      "end_time": 26296.0,
      "text": "According to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26320.0,
      "end_time": 31991.0,
      "text": "the role of storytelling is to mimic life and make us feel emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32150.0,
      "end_time": 35525.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s exactly what storytelling as we know it"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35549.0,
      "end_time": 37144.0,
      "text": "has done very well since then."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38530.0,
      "end_time": 40396.0,
      "text": "But there is a dimension of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41102.0,
      "end_time": 44350.0,
      "text": "that storytelling could never really reproduce."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44875.0,
      "end_time": 47686.0,
      "text": "It is the notion of choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48385.0,
      "end_time": 51152.0,
      "text": "Choices are a very important part of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51176.0,
      "end_time": 55486.0,
      "text": "We as individuals are defined by the choices we make."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55854.0,
      "end_time": 59935.0,
      "text": "Some of our decisions can have very significant consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59959.0,
      "end_time": 62225.0,
      "text": "and totally change the courses of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63433.0,
      "end_time": 67111.0,
      "text": "But in a play, a novel or a film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67135.0,
      "end_time": 71263.0,
      "text": "the writer makes all the decisions in advance for the characters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71287.0,
      "end_time": 73166.0,
      "text": "and as the audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73190.0,
      "end_time": 75844.0,
      "text": "we can only watch, passively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75868.0,
      "end_time": 77991.0,
      "text": "the consequences of his decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79518.0,
      "end_time": 83304.0,
      "text": "As a storyteller, I&#39;ve always been fascinated"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83328.0,
      "end_time": 89133.0,
      "text": "with the idea of recreating this notion of choices in fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89157.0,
      "end_time": 94782.0,
      "text": "My dream was to put the audience in the shoes of the main protagonists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94806.0,
      "end_time": 96547.0,
      "text": "let them make their own decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96571.0,
      "end_time": 100838.0,
      "text": "and by doing so, let them tell their own stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 102811.0,
      "end_time": 108359.0,
      "text": "Finding a way to achieve this is what I did in the past 20 years of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 109512.0,
      "end_time": 114706.0,
      "text": "Today, I would like to introduce you to this new way of telling stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 114730.0,
      "end_time": 118313.0,
      "text": "a way that has interactivity at its heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 119133.0,
      "end_time": 123150.0,
      "text": "Rather than exposing the theory behind it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 123400.0,
      "end_time": 127200.0,
      "text": "which could have been kind of abstract and probably a little bit boring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 132730.0,
      "text": "I thought it would be a great opportunity to do a little experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 133684.0,
      "end_time": 137379.0,
      "text": "I would like you, the people here at TED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 138201.0,
      "end_time": 140928.0,
      "text": "to tell your own story."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 142319.0,
      "end_time": 146686.0,
      "text": "So I came with an interactive scene that we are going to play together."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 147605.0,
      "end_time": 149497.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve asked Vicky --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 149521.0,
      "end_time": 150912.0,
      "text": "hello, Vicky --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 150937.0,
      "end_time": 153411.0,
      "text": "to control the main character for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 153435.0,
      "end_time": 156640.0,
      "text": "And your role -- you, the audience --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 157482.0,
      "end_time": 160278.0,
      "text": "will be to make the choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 160929.0,
      "end_time": 163310.0,
      "text": "So Vicky and I don&#39;t know what&#39;s going to happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 163334.0,
      "end_time": 166717.0,
      "text": "because it will all be based on your decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 168454.0,
      "end_time": 174776.0,
      "text": "This scene comes from our next game, called \"Detroit: Become Human,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 174800.0,
      "end_time": 177702.0,
      "text": "and we are in the near future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 178376.0,
      "end_time": 181860.0,
      "text": "where technology made possible the creation of androids"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 181110.0,
      "end_time": 183410.0,
      "text": "that look exactly like human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 183434.0,
      "end_time": 186619.0,
      "text": "We are in the shoes of this character called Connor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 186643.0,
      "end_time": 187795.0,
      "text": "who is an android,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 187819.0,
      "end_time": 191330.0,
      "text": "and he can do very fancy things with coins, as you can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 191570.0,
      "end_time": 193792.0,
      "text": "He has this blue triangle on this chest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 195560.0,
      "end_time": 198300.0,
      "text": "as all androids do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 198744.0,
      "end_time": 201508.0,
      "text": "and now Vicky is in control of this character."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 201532.0,
      "end_time": 205860.0,
      "text": "She can walk around, she can go anywhere, she can look around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 205110.0,
      "end_time": 207760.0,
      "text": "she can interact with her environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 207100.0,
      "end_time": 209894.0,
      "text": "and now she can tell her own stories by making choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 209918.0,
      "end_time": 212310.0,
      "text": "So here we have our first choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 212334.0,
      "end_time": 214273.0,
      "text": "There is a fish on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 214297.0,
      "end_time": 215463.0,
      "text": "What should we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 215487.0,
      "end_time": 217505.0,
      "text": "Should we save it or should we leave it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 217529.0,
      "end_time": 219502.0,
      "text": "Remember, we are under time pressure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 219526.0,
      "end_time": 220921.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;d better be fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 220945.0,
      "end_time": 222118.0,
      "text": "What should we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222142.0,
      "end_time": 223308.0,
      "text": "Audience: Save it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 223332.0,
      "end_time": 225890.0,
      "text": "David Cage: Save it? Save the fish?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 229808.0,
      "end_time": 230958.0,
      "text": "(Video) (Fish plops)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230982.0,
      "end_time": 232132.0,
      "text": "DC: There we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 233788.0,
      "end_time": 236200.0,
      "text": "OK, we have an android who likes animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 237240.0,
      "text": "OK, let&#39;s move on."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 237264.0,
      "end_time": 239413.0,
      "text": "Remember, we have a hostage situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239804.0,
      "end_time": 243281.0,
      "text": "(Video) Woman: Please, please, you&#39;ve got to save my little girl!"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 243305.0,
      "end_time": 246948.0,
      "text": "Wait -- you&#39;re sending an android?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246972.0,
      "end_time": 249400.0,
      "text": "Officer: All right, ma&#39;am, you need to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 249280.0,
      "end_time": 251346.0,
      "text": "W: You can&#39;t do that!"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 251371.0,
      "end_time": 253810.0,
      "text": "Why aren&#39;t you sending a real person?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 254531.0,
      "end_time": 256334.0,
      "text": "DC: OK, she&#39;s not really happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 256358.0,
      "end_time": 258863.0,
      "text": "Her daughter&#39;s been taken hostage by an android,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 258887.0,
      "end_time": 261790.0,
      "text": "and of course, she&#39;s in a state of shock."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 261103.0,
      "end_time": 263406.0,
      "text": "Now we can continue to explore this apartment."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 263430.0,
      "end_time": 266108.0,
      "text": "We see all the SWAT forces in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 266132.0,
      "end_time": 268248.0,
      "text": "But we need to find this Captain Allen first."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 268272.0,
      "end_time": 270530.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the first thing we need to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270770.0,
      "end_time": 272769.0,
      "text": "So, again, we can go anywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272793.0,
      "end_time": 274948.0,
      "text": "Vicky&#39;s still in control of the character."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 274972.0,
      "end_time": 278467.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see -- oh, I think this is Captain Allen. He&#39;s on the phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279735.0,
      "end_time": 282254.0,
      "text": "(Video) Connor: Captain Allen, my name is Connor."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 282278.0,
      "end_time": 284284.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the android sent by CyberLife."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 287227.0,
      "end_time": 289657.0,
      "text": "Captain Allen: Let&#39;s fire at everything that moves."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 289682.0,
      "end_time": 291470.0,
      "text": "It already shot down two of my men."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292890.0,
      "end_time": 295211.0,
      "text": "We could easily get it, but they&#39;re on the edge of the balcony --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295235.0,
      "end_time": 296420.0,
      "text": "it if falls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 296444.0,
      "end_time": 297649.0,
      "text": "she falls."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 297673.0,
      "end_time": 300943.0,
      "text": "DC: OK, now we need to decide what we want to ask the captain."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 300967.0,
      "end_time": 302211.0,
      "text": "What should be our choice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302235.0,
      "end_time": 304818.0,
      "text": "Deviant&#39;s name? Deviant&#39;s behavior? Emotional shock?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 305590.0,
      "end_time": 308477.0,
      "text": "(Video) C: Has it experienced an emotional shock recently?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 309222.0,
      "end_time": 311445.0,
      "text": "Capt A: I haven&#39;t got a clue. Does it matter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311469.0,
      "end_time": 314450.0,
      "text": "C: I need information to determine the best approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 314654.0,
      "end_time": 317386.0,
      "text": "DC: OK, a second choice. Maybe we can learn something."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 317410.0,
      "end_time": 318563.0,
      "text": "What should we choose?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 318587.0,
      "end_time": 319758.0,
      "text": "Audience: Behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 319782.0,
      "end_time": 321335.0,
      "text": "DC: OK, deviant behavior, Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 321359.0,
      "end_time": 324529.0,
      "text": "(Video) C: Do you know if it&#39;s been behaving strangely before this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 324553.0,
      "end_time": 327631.0,
      "text": "Capt A: Listen ... saving that kid is all that matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 329540.0,
      "end_time": 331808.0,
      "text": "DC: OK, we are not going to learn anything from this guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 331833.0,
      "end_time": 333386.0,
      "text": "We need to do something."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 333410.0,
      "end_time": 336636.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s try to go back in the lobby."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 337806.0,
      "end_time": 341388.0,
      "text": "Oh, wait -- there&#39;s a room over there on your right, Vicky, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341412.0,
      "end_time": 343419.0,
      "text": "Maybe there&#39;s something we can learn here."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 344150.0,
      "end_time": 345608.0,
      "text": "Oh, there&#39;s a tablet."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 346120.0,
      "end_time": 347162.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 353842.0,
      "end_time": 357128.0,
      "text": "(Video) Girl: This is Daniel, the coolest android in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 357153.0,
      "end_time": 358544.0,
      "text": "Say \"Hi,\" Daniel."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 358568.0,
      "end_time": 359722.0,
      "text": "Daniel: Hello!"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 359747.0,
      "end_time": 362155.0,
      "text": "G: You&#39;re my bestie, we&#39;ll always be together!"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 362855.0,
      "end_time": 365940.0,
      "text": "DC: That was just one way of playing the scenes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 365118.0,
      "end_time": 367794.0,
      "text": "but there are many other ways of playing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 367818.0,
      "end_time": 369445.0,
      "text": "Depending on the choices you make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369469.0,
      "end_time": 371518.0,
      "text": "we could have seen many different actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 371542.0,
      "end_time": 373299.0,
      "text": "many different consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 373324.0,
      "end_time": 375414.0,
      "text": "many different outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 375851.0,
      "end_time": 379818.0,
      "text": "So that gives you an idea of what my work is about as an interactive writer."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 379842.0,
      "end_time": 384167.0,
      "text": "Where a linear writer needs to deal with time and space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 384191.0,
      "end_time": 385671.0,
      "text": "as an interactive writer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 385696.0,
      "end_time": 389763.0,
      "text": "I need to deal with time, space and possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 390269.0,
      "end_time": 395830.0,
      "text": "I have to manage massive tree structures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 395107.0,
      "end_time": 398477.0,
      "text": "where each branch is a new variation of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 398501.0,
      "end_time": 401344.0,
      "text": "I need to think about all the possibilities in a given scene"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 401368.0,
      "end_time": 403633.0,
      "text": "and try to imagine everything that can happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 403657.0,
      "end_time": 408527.0,
      "text": "I need to deal with thousands and thousands of variables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 408552.0,
      "end_time": 410747.0,
      "text": "conditions and possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 410771.0,
      "end_time": 414884.0,
      "text": "As a consequence, where a film script is about 100 pages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 415969.0,
      "end_time": 422300.0,
      "text": "an interactive script like this is between four and five thousand pages."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 423319.0,
      "end_time": 427485.0,
      "text": "So that gives you an idea of what this work is about."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 427509.0,
      "end_time": 432940.0,
      "text": "But I think, in the end, the experience is very unique,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 432964.0,
      "end_time": 437920.0,
      "text": "because it is the result of the collaboration"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 437116.0,
      "end_time": 440893.0,
      "text": "between a writer creating this narrative landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 442326.0,
      "end_time": 444233.0,
      "text": "and the player making his own decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 444257.0,
      "end_time": 448467.0,
      "text": "telling his own story and becoming the cowriter"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 448491.0,
      "end_time": 452466.0,
      "text": "but also the coactor and the codirector of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 454772.0,
      "end_time": 459973.0,
      "text": "Interactive storytelling is a revolution in the way we tell stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 459997.0,
      "end_time": 464800.0,
      "text": "With the emergence of new platforms like interactive television,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 464824.0,
      "end_time": 466657.0,
      "text": "virtual reality and video games,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 466681.0,
      "end_time": 468914.0,
      "text": "it can become a new form of entertainment"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 468938.0,
      "end_time": 472574.0,
      "text": "and maybe even a new form of art."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 473427.0,
      "end_time": 476130.0,
      "text": "I am convinced that in the coming years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 476154.0,
      "end_time": 482839.0,
      "text": "we will see more and more moving and meaningful interactive experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 482863.0,
      "end_time": 485411.0,
      "text": "created by a new generation of talents."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 486129.0,
      "end_time": 489860.0,
      "text": "This is a medium waiting for its Orson Welles"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 489110.0,
      "end_time": 490882.0,
      "text": "or its Stanley Kubrick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 490906.0,
      "end_time": 494870.0,
      "text": "and I have no doubt that they will soon emerge"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 494894.0,
      "end_time": 497252.0,
      "text": "and be recognized as such."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 498231.0,
      "end_time": 501107.0,
      "text": "I believe that interactive storytelling can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 501131.0,
      "end_time": 503760.0,
      "text": "what cinema was in the 20th century:"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 504479.0,
      "end_time": 507806.0,
      "text": "an art that deeply changes its time."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 508676.0,
      "end_time": 509834.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 509858.0,
      "end_time": 512576.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}